# Copy to .env.local (gitignored) and fill in. Used ONLY by opt-in Node scripts — never the browser.
# Real AI lyrics provider (opt-in; mock stays the default so the core is $0).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# Runway Gen-4 video/world generation (opt-in; studio/runway.mjs).
